  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      This is a randomized, controlled trial to test the use of an educational video during the
      newborn well-child visit. Parents who watch the video during their medical visit will be
      compared to those parents who receive traditional paper handouts. Measures obtained at
      baseline and 2-week follow-up include knowledge of infant development, self-efficacy with
      infant care, and problem-solving skills.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
